These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: avocado, onion, zucchini, plum, mango, peas, pumpkin
There are 7 different nationalities: british, nigerian, dutch, egyptian, australian, argentine, indian
 1. the person eating zucchini is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating plum is not the argentine##6
 3. the british is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 4. the indian is somewhere to the right of the australian##5
 5. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
 6. the british is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 7. the person eating peas is somewhere between the person eating onion and the nigerian##7
 8. the nigerian is on the left of the indian##1
 9. the egyptian is somewhere between the person eating mango and the dutch##7
10. the dutch is on the left or right of the british##3
11. the australian is on the far left##1
12. the person eating plum is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
13. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person eating peas##5
14. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
15. the person eating mango is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | zucchini    | avocado    | onion | peas | plum | mango    | pumpkin |
| Nationality   | australian | british | dutch  | argentine   | egyptian    | nigerian | indian |

