.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: lime, pumpkin, asparagus, corn, orange, onion, broccoli
The people have 7 different hobbies: fishing, sudoku, magic-tricks, card-games, drawing, photography, video-games
 1. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere between the person eating broccoli and the person eating pumpkin##7
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person eating corn##1
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 5. the person eating lime is somewhere between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is sudoku##7
 6. the person eating onion is somewhere between the person eating corn and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
 7. the person eating orange is somewhere between the person eating corn and the person eating pumpkin##7
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
10. the person eating orange is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
11. the person who's hobby is photography is not the person eating broccoli##6
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
13. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person eating corn##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | broccoli  | asparagus | onion | corn | lime     | orange | pumpkin  |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | photography | sudoku  | video-games  | drawing | card-games      | fishing |

