 3. the fan of disco is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
 4. the fan of classical is somewhere to the right of the fan of dubstep##5
 5. the fan of classical is between the fan of dubstep and the person who's hobby is camping##2
 6. the fan of indie is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere between the fan of folk and the fan of gospel##7
10. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
11. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is camping is not the fan of classical##6
13. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is camping##7
14. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
15. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
16. the person who's hobby is camping is not the fan of dubstep##6
17. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
18. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
19. the fan of classical is somewhere to the left of the fan of folk##5

.:: Answer ::.
