The people use 7 different means of transport: motorbike, subway, roller, tram, boat, car, bus
 1. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
 2. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
 5. the person who's sport is traming is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
 6. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 7. the person driving the roller is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the person driving the boat##7
 8. the person who's sport is traming is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
10. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is cycling##7
12. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
13. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
14. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
15. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
16. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
17. the person driving the tram is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person driving the car##2
18. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not the person driving the bus##6
19. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
